{"tid":98416,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Stat 撚入一入 有條問題想問一問","createTime":"2017-01-28T11:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T12:47:28.000Z","uid":58353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d89506aefea8b27964c13cb2af0e6a01fc4a488f","tid":98416,"uid":58353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"假設有一桶 1L 既水<br />\n有個制可以禁 每禁一下會出 x L咁多水<br />\nx 係uniformly distributed among (0,1) , 0/1 included<br />\n每一次禁水 都係independent event<br />\ni.e. x1 + x2 可以大過 1L <br />\nx1 + x2 + x3 + .... 去到禁哂桶入面既水為止<br />\n問：Expected 要禁幾多下先禁哂所有水？"},{"pid":"5adc2c30feb47c7236a1f79afa15ff952da6039f","tid":98416,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"［0,1］"},{"pid":"c5f94939cde7abb188d96af90212a701c7084c0a","tid":98416,"uid":58353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［0,1］</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76d709df402f6c750b06415054dd295c03176c3","tid":98416,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n呢題係咪stopping time問題？"},{"pid":"2fbcdce026d15e530b8eda197a4f1bd18265f453","tid":98416,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"sum of uniform rv:<br />\n<img src=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irwin%E2%80%93Hall_distribution\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIrwin%25E2%2580%2593Hall_distribution&h=9608b357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本上淨係要 0 &lt;= x &lt;= 1 個pdf<br />\nf_n(x) = x^(n-1)/(n-1)!<br />\n<br />\nP(N&gt;n) = 1/n!<br />\nP(N&lt;=n) = 1 - 1/n!<br />\nP(N=n) = 1/(n-1)! - 1/n! = (n-1)/n!<br />\n<br />\nE(N) = sum from 2 to infty n(n-1)/n!<br />\n= sum from 2 to infty 1/(n-2)!<br />\n= e<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定有無錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5b413827176386a436b8857ec879ee4fce2156","tid":98416,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sum of uniform rv:<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irwin%E2%80%93Hall_distribution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIrwin%25E2%2580%2593Hall_distribution&d=RTsWOQJ2NVSqFPKyJPBKgwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=7cc13763\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irwin%E2%80%93Hall_distribution</a><br />\n基本上淨係要 0 &lt;= x &lt;= 1 個pdf<br />\nf_n(x) = x^(n-1)/(n-1)!<br />\n<br />\nP(N&gt;n) = 1/n!<br />\nP(N&lt;=n) = 1 - 1/n!<br />\nP(N=n) = 1/(n-1)! - 1/n! = (n-1)/n!<br />\n<br />\nE(N) = sum from 2 to infty n(n-1)/n!<br />\n= sum from 2 to infty 1/(n-2)!<br />\n= e<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定有無錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nurl放錯左做貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}